{
  "texts": [
    "For initialization, a random agent is used.",
    "Following the paradigm of online scheduling, the algorithm for integrated scheduling and layout planning is called during the simulation whenever an assembly operation is finished.",
    "As a result, placement and scheduling decisions are fed back to the LMAS, respectively the DES (Fig. 3).",
    "The requirement for real-time decision-making during inference favors using Deep RL for processing data.",
    "The various input data must be encoded to a fixed-size vector representation that NNs can read to handle varying problem sizes."
  ]
}